summary: An email from an FBI agent in New York to a colleague regarding travel to Florida for trial preparation with witnesses, related to the Maxwell trial. It indicates ongoing witness coordination by law enforcement.

events.title: Travel to Florida for Trial Prep
events.description: FBI agents from New York travel to Florida to prepare with several witnesses for the Maxwell trial.

keyFacts: FBI agents were actively preparing witnesses for the Maxwell trial as of July 2021.
The preparation involved travel from New York to Florida to meet with witnesses.
The email originates from the FBI New York Field Office's Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking Desk.
The document reference EFTA00155136 is associated with this communication.
